The paper proposes a model for improving recommendation performance, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. The model uses neural networks, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The model also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it deals with item representations. Finally, the model can be applied to image recommendations (cs.CV) as well.
